description.narrative: UNICEF supported the Government in generating evidence and innovative data solutions to support a child-centred response to the COVID-19 pandemic at national and subnational level. UNICEF released a position paper on the socio-economic impact of COVID-19 on children in Indonesia, and has deployed RapidPro to collect and communicate directly with health and social workers, and teachers to monitor the needs of children and their families during the crisis. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:15/07/2020
